item.title: Basic
item.description: Introduction UAsset Browser is a code plugin for Unreal Engine 4. With UAsset Browser, you can preview uasset thumbnail, view dependency graph between uasset files, inspect/search/filter uasset meta data, and then import uasset file with all it’s dependencies including hard or soft references. Install for Custom Engine Build The process should apply for installing any code plugin installation to a custom engine build. Download suitbale plugin version from Marketplace
